name: Full Body Masked Ape #1
description: I wish you healthy days. Join Our Family And Don't Forget Your Mask! 😷  When you buy a Masked Ape, you’re not simply buying an avatar or a provably-rare piece of art. You are gaining membership access to a club whose benefits and offerings will increase over time. Your Masked Ape can serve as your digital identity, and open digital doors for you.
